### FMOD RECOMMENDATIONS (MERGED)
### ================================

# 1. NEVER ignore FMOD DLLs (we must include them)
!/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/FMOD/**/lib/*

# 2. DON'T ignore FMOD gizmos or editor resources
!/[Aa]ssets/Gizmos/FMOD/*
